## Notes

- **This is the make-or-break milestone.** Test with an actual edit + bash task
  through `claude -p`, not just unit round-trips — the integration is where it
  breaks.
- **Order:** 1 → 2 → 3 give non-streaming tools end to end; 4 (streaming tools)
  depends on M2 plus tickets 1–3; 5 (XML) is optional and can be deferred or
  dropped if your upstream supports native function calling.
- **tool_call_id pairing (ticket 3) is the subtle part.** Anthropic carries ids
  on tool_use/tool_result; OpenAI carries them on tool_calls/tool messages. A
  mismatch silently breaks multi-step agent loops — cover parallel calls in
  tests.
- **Headless project.** Design Refs from DESIGN.md "Intent"; UAT steps are
  CLI/`claude -p` task runs, MANUAL (no browser `[agent-test]`).
- **Optional reference:** teer823/claude-proxy's tool translation + XML mode are
  a structural model — adapt, don't depend.

